=head1 JUDGEMENT

<PRE>
(*1)PASS: The DUID's  format in the Server's Identifier option of Reply 
    message must be base on description of RFC(see above Verification Points).
(*2)PASS: After restarting, the DUID must be keeped.
</PRE>

